# Card (Momentum) — Momentum guidance (Cursor)

**Card** is a **static** layout block for image, header, body, and optional footer. Use it for read-only or lightly interactive regions where **actions** are separate controls (e.g. **`Button`** in footer slots, **`Link`** in **`footer-link`**). The whole card is **not** one big button—use **`CardButton`**, **`CardCheckbox`**, or **`CardRadio`** for selection/click surfaces.

See also: [CardButton](./cardbutton.mdc), [CardCheckbox](./cardcheckbox.mdc), [CardRadio](./cardradio.mdc).

Browse the [Momentum Components catalog](https://momentum.design/en/components/) for naming; Storybook documents props and examples. Reference: [Storybook — Card / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-card--docs). Optional: [Example](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/story/components-card-card--example).

---

## Import

Requires <ThemeProvider> and <IconProvider> ancestors. See setup.mdc.

```jsx
import { Card, Text, Button, Link } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";
```

---

## What it is

- **Layout:** `image` → header (`title` / `subtitle` / up to **3** **`icon-button`** slots) → **`before-body`** / **`body`** / **`after-body`** → footer (**`footer-link`**, **`footer-button-primary`**, **`footer-button-secondary`**, or custom **`footer`**).  
- **Visuals (from `CardComponentMixin`):** **`variant`:** `border` · `ghost` · `promotional` · **`orientation`:** `vertical` · `horizontal` · optional **`iconName`**, **`imageSrc`** / **`imageAlt`**, **`titleTagName`** / **`subtitleTagName`** for semantic headings.  
- **Strings:** **`cardTitle`**, **`subtitle`**—or use **`title`** / **`subtitle`** / **`body`** **slots** for richer content.  
- **Width:** **`--mdc-card-width`** (see Storybook).  
- **No** root **`onClick`**—it is **presentational**.

Use **`Text`** in body slots, **`Button`**, **`Link`** in footer; prefer MDS over raw HTML controls.

---

## Key props (typical)

- **`cardTitle`**, **`subtitle`**, **`variant`**, **`orientation`**, **`imageSrc`**, **`imageAlt`**, **`iconName`**, **`titleTagName`**, **`subtitleTagName`**

---

## Example

Replace **`imageSrc`** with your asset URL or omit **`imageSrc`** / **`imageAlt`** if the design has no image.

```jsx
import { Card, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";


<div role="main">
  <Card
    variant="border"
    orientation="vertical"
    cardTitle="Title"
    subtitle="Subtitle"
    imageSrc="https://picsum.photos/seed/momentum-card/640/360"
    imageAlt="Decorative card image"
    iconName="placeholder-bold"
    titleTagName="span"
    subtitleTagName="span"
  >
    <Text slot="body" tagname="span">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Use Momentum Text for body copy.
    </Text>
  </Card>
</div>
```

Adjust **`slot`** names on children to match Storybook for your installed package version.

---

## Checklist for Cursor prototypes

- [ ] **`ThemeProvider`** + **`IconProvider`** when using **`iconName`** or header icon buttons  
- [ ] **Selection** = **`CardCheckbox`** or **`CardRadio`**; **single CTA** on whole card = **`CardButton`**  
- [ ] **`icon-button` slot:** **max 3** header action buttons  
- [ ] **Footer** uses **`Link`** + **`Button`** (MDS), not raw `<a>` / `<button>` when avoidable  
- [ ] MDS **tokens** for spacing around the card  

Cross-check [Storybook — Card / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-card--docs) and your installed package version.
